The paper deals with fine-grained visual categorization, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed framework involves deep metric learning, which is a machine learning technique (cs.LG) and also involves human-in-the-loop interaction, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with image datasets (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of searching for relevant images on Instagram.
